{"tid":570925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"LEGO迷悼燒炭亡工銀IT主管","createTime":"2018-02-24T07:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T12:14:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"56a3fb603fffc403da7f7aa5d15824c8daa4b977","tid":570925,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:38:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180224/20313741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180224%2F20313741&d=ZSUkDF0cKWt9FWKYi9HxhjANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=b1dfbad8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180224%2F20313741&h=4fbf2609\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180224/20313741</a><br />\n<br />\nLEGO迷悼燒炭亡工銀IT主管<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】在銀行任職信息科技部主管的LEGO大師劉以良（48歲），前日被發現於沙田汽車內燒炭自殺身亡，其遺書透露因工作壓力尋死，中國工商銀行（亞洲）承認劉是他們的員工，表示對其離世深感痛惜，指重視及關心員工的工作壓力及情緒狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180224/large/24la6p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180224%2Flarge%2F24la6p04.jpg&h=a263f578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLEGO大師劉以良前日被發現車內燒炭亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工銀︰重視員工情緒狀況<br />\n<br />\n劉自殺消息震驚香港LEGO界，「香港樂高迷用戶組」fb專頁，以「永遠懷念劉以良」悼念他對樂高界的貢獻，樂高迷曾先生在專頁緬懷劉生前的點滴，「他對LEGO的熱誠，那份情操，深深影響了不少人，亦包括我。」、「請讓大家繼續發揚大師精神，把香港LEGO Afols community繼續發揚光大。」<br />\n<br />\n劉多日前突然離家失蹤，前日被發現在沙田安明街石門站對開一輛掛上P牌的七人車內燒炭自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n工銀亞洲發言人就事件回覆《蘋果》查詢，表示對其離世深感痛惜，並稱已聯繫其家人致以深切慰問，並將提供適切的支援與協助，又謂該行一向重視及關心員工的工作壓力及情緒狀況，日常亦採取多種方式緩解同事工作壓力。<br />\n<br />\n■記者曾海帆"},{"pid":"504f6dd2abc103147f72ccd21f7b8a4aab14791e","tid":570925,"uid":113626,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:39:30.000Z","msg":"銀行撚都幾識做戲<br />\n平時係公司大大力插IT, 一見人死左即做公關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152fa49faa067e0992ac4416e6d633e681d5651f","tid":570925,"uid":3987,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"WFC 垃圾lego死肥宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507cc458ba5f180ac33a3eb8d32ecdeab5a83cf7","tid":570925,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"504f6dd2abc103147f72ccd21f7b8a4aab14791e","tid":570925,"uid":113626,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:39:30.000Z","msg":"銀行撚都幾識做戲<br />\n平時係公司大大力插IT, 一見人死左即做公關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:40:57.000Z","msg":"奴隸總是要有人做"},{"pid":"30851a0b600fc97f13f03accfcb1a6b3253de01c","tid":570925,"uid":17496,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"唔明佢地點諗，壓力大咪辭職囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c63a73f1697da26963043b72f62691e41fe128","tid":570925,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:44:11.000Z","msg":"其實返工有咩事要自殺咁嚴重"},{"pid":"b267d928815128fabdebd1972f34b8a4f8a89a46","tid":570925,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30851a0b600fc97f13f03accfcb1a6b3253de01c","tid":570925,"uid":17496,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"唔明佢地點諗，壓力大咪辭職囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"48歲應該好難轉工？"},{"pid":"165168e723050086efde909473d4804fcd2a1f8c","tid":570925,"uid":57549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"好心icbc咪撚死出黎貓哭老鼠，垃圾公司！！"},{"pid":"b80858f60a623ae6ed2521a83ef23da4d826acd3","tid":570925,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"507cc458ba5f180ac33a3eb8d32ecdeab5a83cf7","tid":570925,"uid":59567,"like":0,"